<http://example.org/req/658#> a owl:Ontology .

<http://example.org/req/658#Req_1_DesignSpec> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Thing,
        ns1:DesignSpecification,
