    ns1:satisfiesRequirement <http://example.org/req/658#Req_0> .

<http://example.org/req/658#ObjSpec_0> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
